  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play][When Digivolving] Reveal the top card of your
    opponent's security stack. If that card is a Digimon card, gain 1 memory. If
    it's a non-Digimon card, \uFF1CDraw 1\uFF1E. Place the revealed card at the top
    or bottom of your opponent\u2019s security stack face down.[All Turns] While
    there's a Tamer, this Digimon gains \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E and can't be deleted
    by your opponent's effects."
